{"type":"message","id":"4d509537","parentId":"7b2c05ca","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:55:02.892Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0bb637bb-765d-4c8a-b721-260619faf16f Tobias Task Watchdog] Run the Tobias task watchdog. Read C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md for context. Execute python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py, inspect its JSON output, and follow this rule strictly: if notifications is empty, reply with exactly NO_REPLY and nothing else. If there are notifications, rewrite each one in clean human Portuguese, concise but informative, and deliver them. Do not send silent confirmations. Do not explain empty scans. Do not invent status.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 29th, 2026 — 12:55 (America/Sao_Paulo) / 2026-03-29 15:55 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774799702825}}
{"type":"message","id":"c777b53e","parentId":"4d509537","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:55:05.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. Read the README.md for context from the task watchdog directory\n2. Execute the watchdog.py script\n3. Inspect its JSON output\n4. If notifications is empty → reply with EXACTLY \"NO_REPLY\" and nothing else\n5. If there are notifications → rewrite each in clean human Portuguese, concise but informative, and deliver them\n6. Do not send silent confirmations, don't explain empty scans, don't invent status\n\nLet me start by reading the README to understand the context.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01LmsV7C5rNUYnbR358cUHHy","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":201,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":740,"totalTokens":16590,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.001005,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.000925,"total":0.0035039000000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774799702959,"responseId":"msg_01Ef7CouTCwW4M2YCZCzExmB"}}
